{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2015-2-28-the-zen-of-python/2015-2-28-the-zen-of-python/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Its my Code Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"28ea1c50-a08c-57b0-9e17-5e2c104f9974","excerpt":"Computer languages should give more prominence to their core philosophy like Python The Zen of Python, by Tim Peters, is only one command away  Beautiful is…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/494d857189a2a33c6a8e20629267340b/f67cc/zen-python.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt text \"\n        title=\"The Zen of Python\"\n        src=\"/static/494d857189a2a33c6a8e20629267340b/88218/zen-python.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/494d857189a2a33c6a8e20629267340b/7237a/zen-python.jpg 148w,\n/static/494d857189a2a33c6a8e20629267340b/0cfdf/zen-python.jpg 295w,\n/static/494d857189a2a33c6a8e20629267340b/88218/zen-python.jpg 590w,\n/static/494d857189a2a33c6a8e20629267340b/f67cc/zen-python.jpg 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>Computer languages should give more prominence to their core philosophy like Python</h1>\n<p>The Zen of Python, by Tim Peters, is only one command away</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">import this</code></p>\n<p>Beautiful is better than ugly.</p>\n<p>Explicit is better than implicit.</p>\n<p>Simple is better than complex.</p>\n<p>Complex is better than complicated.</p>\n<p>Flat is better than nested.</p>\n<p>Sparse is better than dense.</p>\n<p>Readability counts.</p>\n<p>Special cases aren’t special enough to break the rules.</p>\n<p>Although practicality beats purity.</p>\n<p>Errors should never pass silently.</p>\n<p>Unless explicitly silenced.</p>\n<p>In the face of ambiguity, refuse the temptation to guess.</p>\n<p>There should be one— and preferably only one —obvious way to do it.</p>\n<p>Although that way may not be obvious at first unless you’re Dutch.</p>\n<p>Now is better than never.</p>\n<p>Although never is often better than <em>right</em> now.</p>\n<p>If the implementation is hard to explain, it’s a bad idea.</p>\n<p>If the implementation is easy to explain, it may be a good idea.</p>\n<p>Namespaces are one honking great idea — let’s do more of those!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"The Zen of Python","date":"February 28, 2015","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2015-2-28-the-zen-of-python/2015-2-28-the-zen-of-python/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2015-2-18-angularjs-jsamine-spies-and-fakes/2015-2-18-angularjs-jsamine-spies-and-fakes/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AngularJS Jasmine Spies and Fakes"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2015-3-2-so-you-want-a-simple-php-server/2015-3-2-so-you-want-a-simple-php-server/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"So you want a simple PHP Server?"}}}}}